  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK422">
<l>ceṉṟa viṭattāṟ celaviṭā tītorīi</l>
<l>naṉṟiṉpā luyppa taṟivu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Not to permit the mind to go where it lists, to keep it from evil, and to employ it in good, this is wisdom.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
